captions.text: Ro: Hey guys, It's Ro! I'm here with my sister Mo today.

Ro: requested game. And for those of you who don't know
Ro: Egg Roulette is where you take 12 eggs, 8
Ro: of them are hard-boiled, and 4 of them are raw.

Ro: And how you do this is you alternate,
she'll go,
Ro: then I'll go, then she'll go, then I'll go. You pick up an egg
Ro: and you crack it on your head. And the first person to crack
Ro: 2 raw eggs on their head, loses.
